Author: Alright#0419
Content: idea to to have notaries subscribe to who they find trustworthy, if you can get enough notaries to subscribe to you, you can create chain, fund notary addresses and push a new assetchains.json, notaries will see it, build branch(if necessary), sync and start notarizing

Content: not 100% sure it will flesh out exactly as stated though, there's a lot of security concerns in doing this

Content: if you can get min sigs number of notary to agree(shouldn't be easy, should be well-respected well-trusted community members) to notarize whatever you push to your oracle feed, you can add chains to the cluster with ease

Author: Alright#0419
Content: notaries won't have to do anything, as soon as their nodes sees the oracle feed updated, they will start syncing the chain then start notarizing
